xt":"117 Stat. 146","children":[],"tail":"), notwithstanding paragraph (3) of that section, on the date of enactment of the Food, Conservation, and Energy Act of 2008, the Secretary of Agriculture shall transfer $175,000,000” for “Subject to subsection (b), as soon as practicable after the date of enactment of this Act, the Secretary of Agriculture shall transfer $200,000,000” in text and deleted quotation marks before “(1)” and “(2)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/246/s2807/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–246, § 2807(2)","children":[],"tail":", added subsec. (b) and struck out former subsec. (b). Prior to amendment, text read as follows: “The funds described in subsection (a) shall not be used to purchase or lease water rights.”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id79d8d17c-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"id79d8d17d-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Transfer of Funds","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/206/tI/s103"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–206, title I, § 103","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-08-02"},"text":"Aug. 2, 2002","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/116/823"},"text":"116 Stat. 823","children":[],"tail":", provided that not later than 14 days after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-08-02"},"text":"Aug. 2, 2002","children":[],"tail":", the Secretary of Agriculture was to carry out a transfer of funds under former "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/171/